Description:
Auction this Saturday @ 11:00am inspect from 10:30am
Situated in one of Newquay’s most desirable buildings “ THE CONDER “ is this Superb two bedroom apartment bathed in natural light
Offering uninterrupted views toward marina. In excellent condition.
The apartment itself is a spacious 96 m2 approximately and offers the following:
Large open plan living/dining with adjoining balcony, well equipped kitchen with European appliances, two good sized bedrooms master with study ( balcony access ) area, fulll en-suite and w.i.r’s

The magnificent Condor complex offers fully equipped Gymnasium, indoor swimming pool, sauna, large common lawn terrace. Free tram service passes front door with
Melbourne’s CBD only a few minutes away, Harbor Town, Restaurants, Bars & Cafes all virtually on your doors step
Car Park & Storage cage on title complement the apartment

Description:
Spectacular luxurious podium home with breathtaking views
This spectacular and luxurious, three bedroom plus study home boasts panoramic north facing water front views, in Mirvac's newly completed "ARRAY".
Enjoy breathtaking 180 degree sweeping water views of the Dockland harbour and city skyline from a large covered wraparound balcony, perfect for entertaining all year round. Enjoy these magnificent views from all aspects of this spacious home which boasts a large open plan living, dining and entertaining area, Gourmet appointed kitchen, with stone benchtops plus island bench, glass splashback and Miele appliances.
Master bedroom complete with northern orientation and river views, walk in robe, large ensuite with separate bath and toilet. Two further double bedrooms with robes plus a private study, and a central family bathroom.
This brilliant podium home features a private "3" car lock up garage with internal direct access, zoned heating and cooling, separate laundry, opulent designer security entrance. 'Lift access', superb facilities at the "REKDECK" including an onsite gym & fitness centre with pool, spa, steam room and sauna.
Perfectly and conveniently located, just moments to the CBD, Crown Casino, South Warf DFO, Etihad Stadium, easy access to the freeway and all transport options.
Private Appointment only: Contact Brett Graham on 0417 766 777.

Description:
Standout Docklands Pad with an Enormous Balcony
With highlights that include a generous full-length balcony enjoying superb views plus an open living zone that is bathed in natural light, this appealing one bedroom apartment in the Yarra’s Edge precinct is an outstanding entertainer.
This 17th floor dwelling is sure to catch the eye of owner-occupiers and smart investors who are looking to dip their toes in the Docklands property market. The expansive balcony is truly the highlight of the apartment, with an amazing amount of space and marvelous views including glimpses of the CBD and out towards Port Phillip Bay.
Light timber floors and full windows dominate the airy lounge and meals hub, while a gourmet kitchen will have you wanting to always eat in with its stylish stone benchtop, sleek glass splashback, and stainless steel appliances. The spacious bedroom enjoys a great corner position allowing for sensational views (also has balcony access), while further appreciate the pristine bathroom, separate laundry, ducted heat/cool, video intercom, secure car space, and access to RekDek incl. gym, pool, spa, steam room, and sauna.
Enjoy all the amazing amenities and attractions of the wonderful Yarra’s Edge area. South Wharf has great eateries and bars from the Thai flavours of Bangpop to an abundance of beer and bratwurst at Munich Brauhaus. You’re also very close to the world class Crown Entertainment Complex, DFO South Wharf, Capital City Trail, Polly Woodside, Spencer Street trams, and Southern Cross Station.

Description:
Modern and Spacious 26th Floor Beauty Near South Wharf
Get ready to embrace all the contemporary class and relaxed comfort that comes with this excellent two bedroom corner apartment situated in the Yarra Point complex, which has the added bonus of great views including the Yarra River and Port Phillip Bay.
Positioned right next to the green Point Park and displaying stunning space and ultra-chic style, this 26th floor apartment is a genuine delight. Love the light that comes with the open central lounge and dining zone, which is adjoined by a luxury kitchen offering up a stone benchtop and stainless steel appliances including a dishwasher.
The undercover balcony is a magnificent spot to take in the remarkable views, while both bedrooms with built-in robes, impressive bathroom, European laundry, ducted heat/cool, video intercom, and one car space are other extras. You also have access to RekDek incl. gym, pool, spa, steam room, and sauna.
This stylish complex is located in the Yarra’s Edge precinct which is arguably the Dockland’s most coveted area and is perfect for owner-occupiers. Here you’ll have amazing access to all the popular eateries down on South Wharf including The Boatbuilders Yard, The General Assembly, and Munich Brauhaus. You’re also near DFO shopping, Docklands Park, Port Melbourne, and public transport.

Description:
Stunning Location, Stunning Home!
Situated on the 18th floor of the prestigious Victoria Point building in Docklands, this luxury apartment offers residents a picturesque home in the heart of the city.
Strategic design fully facilitates the stunning city surrounds offered by Docklands, with floor to ceiling windows in the living area and both bedrooms allowing direct indoor-outdoor interaction. All windows slide open, extending each room out to the long personal balcony. The kitchen overlooks the living area in an open plan setting, featuring a stainless steel oven, stainless steel dishwasher, stone benchtops, and ample storage space. In pristine condition, the property is ready for its new owners to simply move in and enjoy. A neutral palette throughout serves as the perfect base for the more personal touches. Additional facilities include European-style laundry in the bathroom, integrated heating and cooling, basement parking for one car with a storage cage in the basement.
Victoria Point offers stunning facilities to its residents with a new gym opening soon, concierge reception in the entry foyer and split lift areas with security level access. Placed in the heart of Docklands, one is surrounded by all that Melbourne has to offer in cuisine, bars, shopping and entertainment. Etihad Stadium is just steps away, hosting a myriad of major sporting events and international music acts. It is a short walk to the city, made even shorter by catching a free tram at the doorstep.
The capital city bike trails will take you through the heart of the city or along the Yarra River and down to the beach in just minutes, and when driving, you have quick access to the freeways, in all directions.
Seize this marvellous opportunity while you can, it won’t last long!

Description:
INVESTOR ALERT! A Unique 2 for 1 Docklands Offering!
In one of the Docklands most popular residential buildings and a rare opportunity to purchase two apartments for the price of one, this dual key one bedroom and separate studio apartments are both brilliant examples of modern and light-filled living with amazing views to match. Located near Etihad Stadium, Docklands Park, local cafes, trams, and Southern Cross Station.
Accommodation: With a brilliant net rental return yielding 5.28% (approx.), this is the perfect property for those who want to live in the one bedroom pad and rent out the studio next door. Both apartments boast awe-inspiring views of Melbournes CBD and Port Phillip Bay, while the one bedroom apartment further enjoys a generous living and dining zone, wraparound balcony, stone kitchen with stainless steel appliances, spacious bedroom with BIRs and balcony access, and a pristine bathroom. The studio also boasts a well-sized living and sleeping quarters, sleek kitchen, bathroom, and balcony. Both apartments have central heating and cooling and European laundries.
Features: One secure car space and storage, intercom entry (in both), on-site building manager and concierge services.

Description:
PRICE REDUCED! SUPERB VALUE BRAND NEW APARTMENT AVAILABLE IN CENTRAL DOCKLANDS!
On offer is this amazingly affordable soon to be completed one bedroom plus flexi room apartment located at the new up and coming 888 Collins Street building. Featuring southerly views towards the Yarra River, this modern and cozy apartment comprises of a generous living area, a spacious bedroom and flexi both with natural lighting, and a stylish contemporary bathroom to complete the package.
Within the building itself, the luxury amenities available to residents include indoor pool, gym, spa, library, a smart business lounge, along with a sky garden.
In addition to all that this exciting building has to offer, you will also be situated in a highly desirable position in Victoria Harbour with everything you need at your fingertips; shopping centers, banks, public library, eateries, cafes, post office, medical centers, public transport are all within a two minute walk.
This is an opportunity not to be missed as it will be available to you as brand new, and potential maximum stamp duty savings may still be applicable! Overseas investors welcomed.
888 Collins St is due for completion approximately approx. November 2016.
Please call Peter Doan on 0423 399 999 for more information
